snippet.title: Retimed Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Retimed is a local multiplayer arena shooter with slow-motion.
The game will be available on the Nintendo Switch on September 20th.

eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/retimed-switch
website: https://maniax-games.com/Retimed/
